PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772265857
OL,3,C'Conveyor belt' of airpower: Analyst
OL,4,Cwarns of US military build-up near Iran
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Security Producer
OL,7,FDan Howells
OL,9,FThe cameras that captured USS Gerald R
OL,10,FFord, the biggest and most advanced
OL,11,Faircraft carrier in the American
OL,12,Ffleet, as it left Crete yesterday,
OL,13,Fprovided just the latest visual
OL,14,Fexample of how much US military might
OL,15,Fthere is in the Middle East.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772265857
OL,3,C'Conveyor belt' of airpower: Analyst
OL,4,Cwarns of US military build-up near Iran
OL,6,FThe build-up has been going on for
OL,7,Fweeks, and as the Ford heads into the
OL,8,Feastern Mediterranean, another
OL,9,Fcarrier, the USS Abraham Lincoln, is
OL,10,Falready positioned on the other side
OL,11,Fof the Arabian peninsula, most
OL,12,Frecently spotted in satellite images
OL,13,Foff the coast of Oman on Wednesday.
OL,15,FBut it's not just the aircraft
OL,16,Fcarriers. US fighter jets have been
OL,17,Flanding at bases in Jordan and Israel
OL,18,Ftoo ` adding to what President Trump
OL,19,Fhas called an "armada", a vast
OL,20,Fconcentration of American firepower
OL,21,Fassembled over several weeks.
OL,26,@{D@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772265857
OL,3,C'Conveyor belt' of airpower: Analyst
OL,4,Cwarns of US military build-up near Iran
OL,6,FTaken together, this build-up has led
OL,7,Fmany analysts to conclude that the
OL,8,FUnited States is not just signalling
OL,9,Fstrength, but positioning itself with
OL,10,Fthe capability to launch significant
OL,11,Fstrikes against the Iranian regime at
OL,12,Fshort notice.
OL,14,FAnalysts at the International
OL,15,FInstitute for Strategic Studies
OL,16,Festimate that 10% of available US
OL,17,Fairpower is now in the region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772265857
OL,3,C'Conveyor belt' of airpower: Analyst
OL,4,Cwarns of US military build-up near Iran
OL,6,FResearch fellow Sascha Bruchmann told
OL,7,FITV News: "So the Abraham Lincoln will
OL,8,Fbring in 50 to 60 fighter jets. The
OL,9,FGerald R. Ford probably a little bit
OL,10,Fmore, maybe just closer to 60. There
OL,11,Fare many fighter jets currently parked
OL,12,Fin Jordan at an airbase. We've seen
OL,13,FF35s, specialised planes like the EA18
OL,14,FGrowler and electronic attack
OL,15,Faircraft, F15s, F16s, so approximately
OL,16,Fanother carrier worth of aeroplanes
OL,17,Fjust in Jordan. And then there's some
OL,18,Fconfirmation on satellite imagery that
OL,19,Fwe also have F22s in southern Israel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772265857
OL,3,C'Conveyor belt' of airpower: Analyst
OL,4,Cwarns of US military build-up near Iran
OL,6,F"(That's) probably about 200 to 250
OL,7,Ffighter jets, that tallies up between
OL,8,Fthe carriers and the jets that have
OL,9,Fflown in...that's about just over 10%
OL,10,Fof their total fighters."
OL,12,FOn Thursday's ITV News at Ten
OL,13,Fprogramme, Security Editor Rohit
OL,14,FKachroo looked at what the US's
OL,15,Foptions are
OL,26,@nD@BpmnD@Ipn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772265857
OL,3,C'Conveyor belt' of airpower: Analyst
OL,4,Cwarns of US military build-up near Iran
OL,6,FBut it's not only the fighter jets
OL,7,Fthat analysts have been watching, as
OL,8,Fthe US has been sending other aircraft
OL,9,Fthat could play the key supporting
OL,10,Froles - refuelling tankers, flying
OL,11,Fradar - to places well beyond the
OL,12,FMiddle East.
OL,14,F"There's a significant amount of
OL,15,F(refuelling) tankers between the
OL,16,Fcontinental US along the Atlantic,"
OL,17,FBruchmann added.
OL,26,@wD@ApmwD@Lpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772265857
OL,3,C'Conveyor belt' of airpower: Analyst
OL,4,Cwarns of US military build-up near Iran
OL,6,F"There were pictures on the Azores of
OL,7,Ftankers, and there was traffic in
OL,8,FBulgaria and on Crete. So we see this
OL,9,Fconveyor belt across the Atlantic and
OL,10,Fthe Mediterranean that points towards
OL,11,Fthe Middle East. You not only then
OL,12,Fhave fighter jets, but also very
OL,13,Fexquisite capabilities, signals
OL,14,Fintelligence, electronic intelligence,
OL,15,Fflying communications nodes and flying
OL,16,Fradars."
OL,18,FBruchmann believes this level of US
OL,19,Fresources would support a campaign
OL,20,Fthat could last "a few weeks",
OL,21,Fdepending on the level of intensity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772265857
OL,3,C'Conveyor belt' of airpower: Analyst
OL,4,Cwarns of US military build-up near Iran
OL,6,FHe said: "Last year, we saw two (US)
OL,7,Foperations in the Middle East. One was
OL,8,FMidnight Hammer, which was a one-night
OL,9,Fstrike operation, where really the
OL,10,Ffighter jets enabled a small bomber
OL,11,Ffleet, seven B2 bombers, that was one
OL,12,Fnight. And the other operation was
OL,13,Fcalled Rough Rider, where two aircraft
OL,14,Fcarriers sustained a small campaign
OL,15,Fagainst the Houthis for just under two
OL,16,Fmonths. I think we're looking at
OL,17,Fsomething that kind of merges those
OL,18,Ftwo operations."
OL,26,@nD@apmnD@dpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772265857
OL,3,C'Conveyor belt' of airpower: Analyst
OL,4,Cwarns of US military build-up near Iran
OL,6,F"Trump said it's a mighty armada. Yes,
OL,7,Fit's a formidable force that is there,
OL,8,Fbut it is far from what the US could
OL,9,Fmuster," he added.
OL,11,FThe American embassy in Israel on
OL,12,FFriday announced it was allowing non-
OL,13,Fessential staff to leave the country
OL,14,F"while commercial flights are
OL,15,Favailable", perhaps pointing towards
OL,16,Fconcerns of what an Iranian response
OL,17,Fto an attack might be.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772265857
OL,3,C'Conveyor belt' of airpower: Analyst
OL,4,Cwarns of US military build-up near Iran
OL,6,F"I think primarily the retaliation
OL,7,Fwill be guided towards Israel. It's
OL,8,Fjust the enemy that the Iranians have
OL,9,Fchosen," Bruchmann said.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FWhile Iran still has a significant
OL,17,Farsenal of cruise missiles and attack
OL,18,Fdrones, its ballistic missiles pose
OL,19,Fthe greatest threat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772265857
OL,3,C'Conveyor belt' of airpower: Analyst
OL,4,Cwarns of US military build-up near Iran
OL,6,F"Iran has a significant number of
OL,7,Fballistic missiles," Bruchmann added.
OL,8,F"On the one hand, Israel has
OL,9,Fformidable defences, but it's about
OL,10,Fthis interceptor versus ballistic
OL,11,Fmissile math. There can always be some
OL,12,Fthat go through.
OL,14,F"Last year, we saw intercept rates of
OL,15,F90%, which are phenomenal for missile
OL,16,Fdefence systems. But that still means
OL,17,Fthat 10% go through."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772265857
OL,3,C'Conveyor belt' of airpower: Analyst
OL,4,Cwarns of US military build-up near Iran
OL,6,FIsrael was able to strike some of
OL,7,FIran's ballistic missile stockpiles
OL,8,Fand launchers last year. But a lot is
OL,9,Fstill not known about Iran's ability
OL,10,Fto have replenished its stockpiles.
OL,12,FBruchmann said: "We don't know for
OL,13,Fcertain how many missiles have
OL,14,Fsurvived on the Iranian side. There's
OL,15,Fan Israeli estimate that says
OL,16,Fsomething like 1,500 medium-range
OL,17,Fballistic missiles and about 100 to
OL,18,F200 launchers remain."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772265857
OL,3,C'Conveyor belt' of airpower: Analyst
OL,4,Cwarns of US military build-up near Iran
OL,6,FBut there are potential targets closer
OL,7,Fto Iran, within range of its shorter-
OL,8,Frange ballistic missiles. The US has a
OL,9,Fnumber of bases - as well as allies -
OL,10,Fon the other side of the Persian Gulf.
OL,12,F"The short-range ballistic missiles
OL,13,Fare a headache," Bruchmann said.
OL,15,FEven less is known about how many of
OL,16,Fthese shorter-range missiles Iran has;
OL,17,Fthey are harder to track and can be
OL,18,Fstored underground, though Bruchmann
OL,19,Fsays Iran potentially has thousands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772265857
OL,3,C'Conveyor belt' of airpower: Analyst
OL,4,Cwarns of US military build-up near Iran
OL,6,FWhile their warheads are smaller than
OL,7,Ftheir longer-range counterparts and
OL,8,Fthey do less damage, they may be
OL,9,Fharder to defend against over a large
OL,10,Farea like the Gulf.
OL,12,F"The flight times are shorter, the
OL,13,F(missile) profiles are lower, and Iran
OL,14,Fhas more of these missiles and over a
OL,15,Fshorter distance they're also a bit
OL,16,Fmore precise. So it's really the
OL,17,Fquestion of having more of these
OL,18,Fmissiles, that can hit more precisely,
OL,19,Fagainst a limited (defensive)
OL,20,Fcapacity. And that missile math
OL,21,Fworries me.
OL,26,@uD@ApmuD@Ipn{D@Spm{D@]pn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772265857
OL,3,C'Conveyor belt' of airpower: Analyst
OL,4,Cwarns of US military build-up near Iran
OL,6,F"No, but you know, the problem is they
OL,7,Fare really much harder to track
OL,8,Fbecause they can store them
OL,9,Funderground, the solid fuel. You don't
OL,10,Fhave to take them out, fuel them up,
OL,11,Fand shoot them like, you know, so it.
OL,12,FYeah, the short-range ballistic
OL,13,Fmissiles are a headache."
OL,15,FYou can hear Talking Politics wherever
OL,16,Fyou get your podcasts, including Apple
OL,17,FPodcasts and Spotify, and watch every
OL,18,Fepisode on YouTube and ITVX.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/15
